Need to re-build BL2 and TFM when:

1. Partition of partition offset is changed.
2. BL2 partition offset
3. TFM partition offset
4. PS partition size //TODO optimized
5. ITS partition size //TODO optimized

6. ECDSA/RSA key method is changed, default to ECDSA
7. XIP or OVERWRITE is changed, default to OVERWRITE
8. secureboot vs legacyboot, default to secureboot

Also pay attention that:
1. TFM test stuites  
